controls

Class ZoomSlider

  • java.lang.Object
    • controls.ZoomSlider

  • public class ZoomSlider
extends java.lang.Object
    Class ZoomSlider implements slider at the right side of the application. It's purpose is to change values of map scaling. Each change of value is send to the MapPane object, that should immediately modify it's scaling property.
    Author:
    Michal Rein, Ondřej Motyčka
